text: Larry Murphy (born 1972 in Clonroche, County Wexford) is an Irish sportsperson. He plays hurling with his local club Cloughbawn and was a member of the Wexford senior inter-county team from 1992 until 2004. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Cloughbawn hurlers Category:Wexford inter-county hurlers
title: Larry Murphy (hurler)
